title: Putting green, Car wash, Wood Floors, Covered Parking!
posting_body: Convenient to DART RAIL Green Line & The Colony * Racquetball & Basketball * Garages *
A fantastic place to call home!
Our apartment homes offer unique interiors including plank flooring, crown molding, ceiling fans with lights, mirrored closet doors, built-in desks and shelves and full-size washer/dryer connections.
Take advantage of the sports club at your doorstep: two resort-style pools and spa, indoor basketball and racquetball, putting green, sand volleyball and fitness center with HDTV.
Spectacular amenities include movie theater, arcade game room, two-stall car wash, business center with high-speed Internet and fully-equipped playground.
Covered parking, garages and enclosed backyards are available as is WiFi in the clubhouse, business center and poolside.
Please call Desiree at Dash Apartment locators
